[[File:Jose Medina.png|thumb]]<big>Jose '''Medina (1914-) His mother is Mariangel Medina (1894-1923), he unfortunately didn't know his father, nor did he have a brother. During his childhood, he liked playing soldier with his friends and he got into trouble a lot. During his early childhood, he got a new stepfather named Dante Vasquez, and when he was 4 got a Staffordshire Bull terrier named Spike.'''</big>

== Early life ==
At, age 2 he got a stepfather Dante Vasquez, a 24-year old unemployed person (1899-) they went to Hongkong for their honeymoon. He got a new, Staffordshire named Spike (1908-). At age, 5 he suffered a mild ear infection. At age 6, he got enrolled into Valentina Alvarez Primary School, a public school. At age, 7 he came back home from school to notice Spike escaped, so he looked for him, and found him across the street. At age, 28 while lighting fireworks, one of the fireworks were faulty, and while his mom set them up it exploded and killed her instantly, Jose and his stepfather attended her funeral, at age 9 after the sadden unfortunate he took a walk to calm himself down. Around, age 10 Spike passed away in his sleep. At age 13, in music class he played the violin, at age 14 he skipped school, and helped girl cheat on her test, around that year he started dating a girl named Carmen Ramos, at age 15 he got pneumonia bedridden, once he got better age 16, he got a part time job as  a newspaper delivery person, unfortunaly Carmen broke up with him so he just let it slide. At age 18, he graduated, and quit his part time job, and got into the army.

== Military career ==
At, age 19 he got promoted to Private second class, with a salary of $7,208. The next year he got into deployment to a treacherous region of south Africa, he served his country by successfully completing it and got a award of honor. At age, 21 he got promoted to Private First class with a salary of $8,064. Shortly, months after his 23rd birthday he got promoted to Specialist. After, he walked 5 grueling miles of marching in the desert, his mind was delirious, His feet are blistering, and he is falling behind the rest of the platoon, so he caught up. At around age 35, he got promoted to Sergeant Major with a salary of $25,927. He served his country by, completing a deployment to hostile territory deep within Serbia. He screamed at a fellow soldier to stop just before she was about to pick up a IED.  His platoon starts taking heavy fire when suddenly his M4 rifle jams, At age, 59 he grabbed his backup pistol after. Around age 62, he retired from the Mexican Army.

== Personal life ==
At age 19, he got cured of depression. Around age 21, he dated a girl named Paula Molina. They then took it to the next level., At age, 26 she proposed and at age 27 they got married. At age 28 he got pregnant. And named him after his grandpa Sebastian, he became good friends with a man named Dante Gomez.  He took his son to vaccinate him. At age 32, he got pregnant, and she gave birth to a baby boy named Daniel Medina. At age 27 he got her pregnant again, and gave birth to a baby boy named Pepe, fortunately he got pregnant again the next year, and his wife gave birth to a baby girl named Andrea. At 45, his son, Sebastian got diagnosed with Cancer of the testicle. Unfortunaly, when he was 47 after Sebastian's battle with cancer he passed away, in his hospital room a few weeks after his 18th birthday, At the age of 50, his other son Pepe got diagnosed with the same cancer, he didn't want his other son to die, his stepfather passed away from suffering a stroke, and after a lot of treatment his son is no longer suffering from cancer (also is this genetics-). He identified as Bisexual, at age 61. At age 66 he moved to Italy, divorcing her, before dating Bria Sozzani. At age 70, he started drinking Vodka.  At age, 75 he almost got broken up by his girlfriend., and he broke up with her. At age 81, he tried Adderall, a year before his death.



== Sicknesses ==
At, age 5 he suffered a mild ear infection. At, age 15 he got diagnosed with a "bad" case Pneumonia. At age 40, he got diagnosed with Pink eye.


== Death ==
On December, 25th while celebrating a Christmas party he fell asleep and passed away in his sleep, His sons tried to wake him up but it was too late. His funeral was on December 31st, and his three loving children attended. His net worth was $529,534. R.I.P Jose Medina.
